        <num>45-4-8</num>
        <content>
          <p>No attorney at law or county officer shall be accepted as surety on the bond of any county officer.</p>
          <p>(Ga. L. 1876, p. 13, § 1; Code 1882, § 152; Civil Code 1895, § 248; Civil Code 1910, § 283; Code 1933, § 89-416.)</p>
